🥹“Two months of hard work and beautiful moments. 
We used to start our day with alottt of deep discussions… dimaag toh bahut tez tha sabka lekin class mai aakar chill ho jaate the. 
.
Phir shuru hoti thi serious class aur uss beech bhi agar shivuu ko dekh liya toh koi serious nahi reh pata☺️, kavya ki munching all the time, sabko kheela k rakhti thi, divya ki pyari smile for no reason 🙈.. kushal ki energy bhari vibes and his helping nature ne toh sabka dil jeet liya and krishna ka statement “jab bhi power jaaye kaam ki baatein shuru kardo” 
Ohhh I really miss that all, Neha toh wait karti thi aaj mam k liye kya lekar jana hai, thnx neha 😘 … khushi k haath ka khana, pragya ki perfection took my heart, deepali ki wo awaj ”areyyy didi inhe toh dekhlo zara” khushi ki cute smile, aur meri pareshan ladki jham-jham ☺️… Meri jaishree k dedication,  priti ka power and positivity, rone badi jaldi lag jaati hai bas. Ohhh saumya ka kimti Phone.. I’m gonna miss this alott… mansi ki care…surbhi k nuskhe. 🥰 Cheena ki chi-chi.. kuch bhi kaho hasaa deti thi sabhi ko. Sakshi ki mehnat…bhuke pyaase lage rehti thi. Dono Payal ki lajavaab progress. Aashi k nonstop practice. And Most importantly sabke eyes k issues 🙈.. oh god what a beautiful memories 🥹

I am so glad to have such an amazing bunch of creative students. 
I am so proud of each one of you. Thank you for the memories and for being amazing. This is just the start of your journey my TALENTED  STARS✨ 
I LOVE U THE MOSTTTTTT & I am gonna miss u all my life. 🥹🤗
